Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.27,0:00:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Doppel Ranger Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.48,0:00:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.92,0:00:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I kicked you! Fall over!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.62,0:00:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,My evil empire is planning to\Ntake over the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.92,0:00:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't be defeated that easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.39,0:00:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,In the TV show, we always\Ndefeat you at the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.16,0:00:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Are your plans for world domination\Ngoing well?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.10,0:00:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Johan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.64,0:00:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not falling over at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.04,0:00:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Things will be rough after you\Ntake over the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.68,0:01:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of world are you\Ngoing to make?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.05,0:01:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care.\NI'm finished after I mess it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.18,0:01:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! It sounds like more fun\Nto mess it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.42,0:01:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll quit the Rainbow Rangers\Nand join the evil organization!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.26,0:01:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, shall we start\Nheading back?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.33,0:01:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.37,0:01:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's all head back.\NDon't forget anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.95,0:03:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's getting a bit warmer, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.99,0:03:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.36,0:03:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Rosemary catch a cold\Nthis past winter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.96,0:03:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. She was running around\Noutside with her friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.07,0:03:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,She gets a terrible fever every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.87,0:03:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it was around this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.31,0:03:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We had to rush to the doctor\Nin the middle of the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.51,0:03:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you always carry around\Npictures of her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.78,0:03:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. She's probably gotten big.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.09,0:03:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,She's growing, so her face
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.82,0:04:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,has probably changed\Nduring the time we've been apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.06,0:04:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But I know that I'll be able to\Nrecognize Rosemary,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.96,0:04:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter how big she gets.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.90,0:04:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.87,0:04:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Show her this when\Nyou think it's appropriate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.14,0:04:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,They're newspaper clippings\Nand a copy of the report
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.51,0:04:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,from when I shot\Nthat young serial killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.65,0:04:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to ask you to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.52,0:04:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is that I killed someone.\NI'm not justifying my actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.16,0:04:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that I want her\Nto know the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.20,0:04:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.61,0:04:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,When...can I meet her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.31,0:05:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll ask her once more\Nif she wants to meet her father.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.65,0:05:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I see ! I'll be waiting for a call !\NI return home every night at 9:00!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.99,0:05:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Richard, you're back\Nto your old self again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.16,0:05:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.03,0:05:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You have the same look in your eyes\Nas when you were younger...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.80,0:05:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,When you first became\Na detective... When we first met.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.45,0:05:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.42,0:05:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think? You'll get a bonus\Nif you sign up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.32,0:05:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we already have insurance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.52,0:05:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Just listen to what I have\Nto offer, Mr. Liebert.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.49,0:05:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The insurance I have right now\Nis enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.46,0:05:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't afford another policy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.67,0:05:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We bought a policy four years ago\Nwhen we moved in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.57,0:05:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Four years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.14,0:05:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Where were you living before then?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.81,0:06:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,In Bruntál, near Mannheim.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.68,0:06:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Bruntál, huh? That's a nice place.\NAre you from there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.02,0:06:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. We lived there\Nbefore coming here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.72,0:06:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, ma'am,\Ndo you have any children?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.29,0:06:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, our son is currently attending\Nthe University of Munich.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.62,0:06:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,A college student!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.36,0:06:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, I have a policy\Nthat's perfect for young people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.96,0:06:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Just hear me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.46,0:06:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.63,0:06:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.87,0:06:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this your son?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.90,0:06:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He was very cute. What's his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.97,0:06:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Johan. Would you like some tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.81,0:06:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. ..you don't have to.\NDon't mind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.34,0:06:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He only calls once in a while\Nnow that he attends the university.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.42,0:06:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how boys are.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.42,0:06:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Boring, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.17,0:06:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back, Dr. Reichwein.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.57,0:07:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, to Johan's home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.17,0:07:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Well, they were\Na pretty ordinary family.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.45,0:07:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So what do you think, Richard?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.58,0:07:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, my experience\Nas a police detective tells me that
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.22,0:07:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,the more ordinary something is,\Nthe more suspicious I should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.86,0:07:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.46,0:07:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I'm going to do more\Nresearch on Johan's acquaintances.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.20,0:07:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Something...\NThere's got to be something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.87,0:07:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan's prep school report\Ndescribes him as
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.44,0:07:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,a well-behaved student\Nwith good grades.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.51,0:08:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I know that I'll be\Nable to recognize Rosemary,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.21,0:08:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}no matter how big she gets.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.76,0:08:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That baby's face... It couldn't have\Ngrown up to become Johan!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.10,0:08:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. This is the birth certificate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.11,0:08:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.81,0:08:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Johan Wilhelm Liebert...\NBorn February 9, 1976...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.32,0:08:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He was definitely born in this town.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.82,0:09:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nothing... out of the ordinary.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.66,0:09:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Hertz!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.36,0:09:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.23,0:09:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,How many times must I tell you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.20,0:09:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No smoking in this office!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.83,0:09:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so stiff. Get me an ashtray.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.70,0:09:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.77,0:09:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a fire here\Nfour years ago, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.17,0:09:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We've had such a terrible time\Nsince then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.47,0:09:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,All of our documents were destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.78,0:09:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you redo all the documents?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.61,0:09:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.81,0:09:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We had to have people give us\Ntheir information to redo everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.68,0:09:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a small town, so we were able to\Nget everything back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.63,0:09:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, thanks for coming, Dr. Gillen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.07,0:09:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while, Dr. Reichwein.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.48,0:09:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma appeared before you
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.95,0:09:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and said that he was looking\Nfor a man named "Johan"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.92,0:10:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. He didn't have any grounds\Nfor anything he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.89,0:10:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But if this person is the "friend"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.19,0:10:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,who incited Peter Jurgens,\Nthe serial killer I'm researching,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.23,0:10:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll be able to find a clue\Nto all these cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.10,0:10:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of it, Dr. Gillen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.34,0:10:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I'll get permission to interview\NJurgens as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.17,0:10:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be able to prove\NDr. Tenma's innocence
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.04,0:10:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,based on his reaction\Nto this photograph.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.70,0:11:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He's dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.16,0:11:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. The real Johan Liebert,\Nwho was born in Bruntál,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.63,0:11:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,died when he was two years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.40,0:11:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean that the Lieberts
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.37,0:11:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,used the fact that the office's records\Nhad been destroyed
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.08,0:11:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,to pretend that their son\Nwas still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.78,0:11:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.78,0:11:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.42,0:11:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The Johan Liebert\Nwho exists right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.22,0:11:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Who in the world...is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.72,0:11:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,At any rate. .. As I told you, I've given\NDr. Gillen a photo of Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.80,0:11:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hope to get an answer from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.13,0:12:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,How about some dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.10,0:12:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I've got to get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.97,0:12:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Going back to work\Nafter running around all day?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.88,0:12:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I might get a phone call.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.61,0:12:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I may be able to meet my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.52,0:12:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.99,0:12:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right. What's important is that\NI move forward...right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.79,0:12:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! You've completely recovered!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.97,0:12:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?! Hello?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.44,0:12:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dad? It's me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.49,0:12:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Rosemary...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.32,0:12:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm doing fine. Yes... Yeah\NOf course I can see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.13,0:13:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see you.. .at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.70,0:13:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Richard...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.07,0:13:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.64,0:13:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This boy. Jurgens...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.18,0:13:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you seen him before?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.18,0:13:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you met him before?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.25,0:13:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.42,0:13:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You said that your friend Johan\Nonly sent you letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.56,0:13:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That you'd never met.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.83,0:13:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But Johan knew a lot about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.01,0:13:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Could I borrow your pen?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.91,0:13:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Sorry, but I'm not allowed\Nto give things to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.58,0:13:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Lend me the pen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.00,0:14:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The park.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.77,0:14:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.17,0:14:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The park. It was the day\Nafter I had killed someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.27,0:14:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking, "I'm going to quit.\NThis is going to be the last time."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.41,0:14:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.21,0:14:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He was with a lot of children.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.58,0:14:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on a second.\NI forgot to rewind the tape!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.32,0:14:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Start over from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.79,0:14:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,"Come with us."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.59,0:14:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.23,0:14:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,"Come with us."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.39,0:14:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,"Come with us."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.56,0:14:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,"Come with us."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.77,0:14:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,"Come with us."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.70,0:14:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,"Come..."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.72,0:15:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What do you want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.22,0:15:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We met at Mr. Schuwald's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.49,0:15:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Johan Liebert. I called you\Nseveral times and you didn't answer,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.46,0:15:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,so I came to see you in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.50,0:15:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes? Ah, Dr. Gillen.\NHow was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.61,0:15:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened when\Nyou showed Jurgens the photo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.92,0:15:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He's dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.48,0:15:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Just now in the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.39,0:15:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The police are questioning me\Nright now, so I can't go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.72,0:15:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Our key witness is dead
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.59,0:15:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,because I was careless enough\Nto give him a pen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.30,0:15:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Dr. Reichwein, his suicide
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.10,0:15:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,was clearly a response\Nto Johan's photograph!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.94,0:15:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll come over after\Nthey're finished questioning me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.47,0:16:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!\NI'll contact Richard immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.48,0:16:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Richard...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.99,0:16:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A college paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.09,0:16:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I'm researching the Convention\Non the Rights of the Child,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.53,0:16:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,which was formed in 1989 by the U.N.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.24,0:16:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like something to drink,\NMr. Richard?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.60,0:16:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.17,0:16:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You quit drinking, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.31,0:16:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.45,0:16:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You were drunk\Nand executed that boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.49,0:16:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.55,0:16:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah. I was drunk,\Nand I did something unforgivable.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.29,0:16:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to know something\Nrelated to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.60,0:16:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The boy you killed. ..\NStephan Yoss, age seventeen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.70,0:17:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What crime did he commit?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.14,0:17:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy, huh? A seventeen-year-old boy\Ncommitted those demonic crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.38,0:17:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Nine counts of rape and murder,\Ntwo counts of attempted murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.51,0:17:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that why you executed him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.98,0:17:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't an execution!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.08,0:17:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. ..sorry. By the way,\Nyou are aware that Article 40
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.22,0:17:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,of the Convention on the Rights\Nof the Child states that every child is
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.89,0:17:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,"to be presumed innocent until proven\Nguilty according to law"' aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.80,0:17:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know. I was once\Nin the juvenile department.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.97,0:17:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.90,0:17:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So what about Article 37?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.90,0:17:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,"Neither capital punishment\Nnor life imprisonment"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.17,0:17:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,"without possibility of release\Nshall be imposed for of fences"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.74,0:17:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,"committed by persons\Nbelow eighteen years of age."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.48,0:17:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Most of the convention concerns\Nbasic human rights,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.48,0:17:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,which are given to people\Nof this country regardless of age.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.49,0:17:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I did not set out to execute him!\NIt was a drunken mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.49,0:17:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it is something\NI cannot take back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.63,0:17:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I've accepted\Nsociety's judgment and...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.53,0:18:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now, just hold on a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.43,0:18:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to meet you\Nin order to write my paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.34,0:18:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry if I upset you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.31,0:18:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we take a walk\Nfor a change of pace?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.91,0:18:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like this whiskey.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.11,0:18:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The night air is still chilly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.02,0:18:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Dr. Gillen, I still haven't\Nbeen able to contact Richard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.72,0:18:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He said that he might be\Nable to see his daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.86,0:18:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think he'd be meeting her\Nthis late at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.63,0:18:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, when you get a hold of him,\Ntell him to move with caution.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.30,0:18:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm heading over right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.47,0:18:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Stephan Yoss's history. ..\NDo you know about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.11,0:18:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe. ..he was in an orphanage\Nin East Germany when he was young,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.81,0:18:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,or something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.41,0:18:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to know more.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.82,0:18:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the most important thing\Nwhen talking about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.32,0:19:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The orphanage he was in.. .\NIt was a horrible place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.56,0:19:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a good kid.\NBut horrible things happened to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.07,0:19:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The way his mind was warped there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.04,0:19:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Convention on the Rights of the Child,\NArticle 6.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.74,0:19:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Rights to life, and assurance\Nof survival and development.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.41,0:19:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Article 8. Preservation of identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.41,0:19:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Article 19. Protection from abuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.88,0:19:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It was a demonic place
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.19,0:19:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,where no one was concerned\Nwith such things.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.12,0:19:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The place was called 511 Kinderheim.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.56,0:19:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be able to see your\Ndaughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.00,0:19:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.17,0:19:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know about her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.10,0:19:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that your daughter calling you\Nat your house?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.64,0:19:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be able to see her?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.31,0:19:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.72,0:20:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What's. ..your motive?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.62,0:20:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,To write a paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.86,0:20:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.39,0:20:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your motive for staying\Nat Schuwald's place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.46,0:20:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Who... Who...are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.74,0:20:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You said that you were drunk\Nwhen you shot that boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.51,0:20:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer my question first!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.12,0:20:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,On that day, you were seen drinking\Nat a bar after you had killed the boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.39,0:20:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But isn't that strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.59,0:20:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,As far as I can determine,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.70,0:20:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,there isn't a single person who saw\Nyou drinking before you killed that boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.34,0:20:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You weren't drunk\Nwhen you shot that boy, were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.21,0:21:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.64,0:21:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You were sober. You were calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.78,0:21:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You calmly pulled that trigger\Nin order to execute him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.66,0:21:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.39,0:21:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.39,0:21:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you trying to forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.00,0:21:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Or are you lying?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.33,0:21:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you lying to other people?\NOr to yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.07,0:21:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you certain that\Nhe committed his crimes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.81,0:21:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you have the right to execute\Nhim?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.75,0:21:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think that by lying,\Nyour sins will go away?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.96,0:21:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What a serious crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.69,0:21:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Can someone who's done\Nsuch a serious crime
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.83,0:21:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,really face his daughter\Nand act as if he's been rehabilitated?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.64,0:22:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.15,0:22:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Want a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.45,0:22:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Gillen? Is that Dr. Gillen?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.96,0:22:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.56,0:22:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Your patient, Richard Braun...is dead.
